{"id":46367,"date":"2025-12-23T21:39:29","date_gmt":"2025-12-23T18:39:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/e-museum.kz\/exhibit\/68da7f081f14aa8ef-en\/"},"modified":"2025-12-31T12:52:30","modified_gmt":"2025-12-31T09:52:30","slug":"68da7f081f14aa8ef-en","status":"publish","type":"exhibit","link":"https:\/\/e-museum.kz\/en\/exhibit\/68da7f081f14aa8ef-en\/","title":{"rendered":"Medal &#171;Thirty Years of Victory in the Great Patriotic War of 1941-1945&#187;"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>A round medal measuring 36 mm in diameter.On the obverse of the medal, against the background of festive fireworks, there is a relief image of the sculpture of E. V. Vuchetich &#171;Motherland&#187;. To the left of the sculpture, a five-pointed star and the date &#171;1945-1975&#187; are depicted on a laurel branch descending downwards. On the reverse side of the medal are placed: in the upper part along the circumference the inscription &#171;TO the PARTICIPANT of the WAR&#187;, in the middle \u2014 the inscription &#171;XXX years of Victory in the Great Patriotic War of 1941-1945&#187;, in the lower part \u2014 a relief image of a hammer and sickle on a ribbon. The edges of the medal are bordered by a rim. The images and inscriptions on the medal are convex. The medal is connected by means of an eyelet and a ring to a pentagonal block covered with a 24 mm wide silk moire ribbon with longitudinal alternating stripes of black and orange with a width of 3 mm each, red with a width of 10 mm, green and red with a width of 3 mm each. The edges of the ribbon are edged with narrow orange stripes.<br \/>\nDimensions: diameter \u2013 3.2 cm, height with pad &#8212; 8 cm.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","